
**purifying or cleaning the fullers earth it is disolved in pure rain water filtered and kept in the hot sun for evaporation the resulting salt is again dissolved in rain water filtered and evaporated as before thus it is repeated ten times**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   தசதீட்சை
